race.comment: VERY BEST BUDDY (1) is worth forgiving last start after finishing eighth (20.49) from Box 3 at this track over 340m. Has won two of four starts from this draw. Better than last start and worth following up. TRAIN TICKET (3) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (20.32) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Worth another chance. WE'LL SEE (5) has missed the frame at his last couple but did finish in the minors in quick time three back (25.25) at this track in a Grade 5. Has the ability and expected to do much better. IMPRESS UBUD (7) can fill a top-three spot.
